    • isNewerJavaVersionRequired

      public boolean isNewerJavaVersionRequired()
      Tells whether or not this add-on requires a newer Java version to run.

      The requirement might be imposed by a dependency or the add-on itself. To check which one use the methods getAddOn() and getAddOnMinimumJavaVersion().

      Returns:
      true if the add-on requires a newer Java version, false otherwise.

    • hasMissingLibs

      public boolean hasMissingLibs()
      Tells whether or not this add-on has missing libraries (that is, not present in the file system).

      The issue might be caused by a dependency or the add-on itself. To check which one use the methods getAddOn() and getAddOnMissingLibs().

      Returns:
      true if the add-on has missing libraries, false otherwise.
      Since:
      2.9.0
